The paper discusses the recent research progress in graphics on geometry, structure, and semantic analysis of 3D indoor data, as well as different modeling techniques for creating plausible and realistic indoor scenes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GR (Computer Graphics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions human-centric scene analysis and modeling, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
